videos.headline: McMillian gets lost in snow on 13-yard TD
videos.description: The Buffaloes strike first in snowy Colorado as Travon McMillian pounds his way into the end zone on a 13-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Montez's deep snowball picked off by Utah
videos.description: Colorado QB Steven Montez lets a deep ball rip into the snowy air and is intercepted by Utah's Marquise Blair.

videos.headline: Referee orders fans not throw snowballs on field
videos.description: The lead official of Utah vs. Colorado interrupts play to order fans not to throw snowballs onto the field.

videos.headline: Shelley slings deep TD to Dixon
videos.description: Utah QB Jason Shelley uncorks a deep ball that lands in the lap of Jaylen Dixon for a 47-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Shyne plows in Utah TD
videos.description: Armand Shyne gets the call on 1st-and-goal and bulldozes into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown, extending Utah's lead to 27-7 over Colorado.
